# 📚 AI-Powered Research Paper Summarizer & Insight Extractor

## 🚀 Overview
This project presents an AI-powered research assistant capable of analyzing academic and industry research papers. It automates the process of summarization, enables intelligent semantic search, and visualizes relationships between key concepts using a knowledge graph.

---

## 🎯 Outcomes
- Automated summarization of research papers
- Extraction of key concepts, methodologies, and findings
- Construction of a knowledge graph for relationship mapping
- Semantic search across large research datasets
- Interactive dashboards for exploration and structured insights

---

## 🏗️ Modules

### 📄 1. Document Ingestion & Parsing Layer
- Ingests research papers from PDFs and online repositories (e.g., arXiv, PubMed)
- Parses documents into structured text
- Extracts metadata such as title, authors, and citations

---

### 🧠 2. Summarization & Insight Extraction Engine
- Uses Transformer-based models (BART, T5, LLaMA)
- Generates abstractive summaries of research papers
- Extracts key insights such as:
  - Core findings
  - Methodologies
  - Important metrics

---

### 🔍 3. RAG + Semantic Search Layer
- Implements Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
- Uses LangChain with FAISS/Pinecone for vector search
- Enables natural language querying across research papers
- Retrieves contextually relevant information

---

### 🔗 4. Knowledge Graph Builder
- Extracts entities such as authors, topics, and institutions
- Identifies relationships between entities
- Stores and queries graph data using Neo4j

---

### 📊 5. Visualization & Dashboard Hub
- Interactive dashboards for:
  - Semantic search results
  - Knowledge graph exploration
  - Research summaries
- Supports exporting reports in PDF/Excel format

---

## 🔄 Project Flow

The system follows a structured pipeline to process research papers and generate intelligent insights:

Research Papers (PDFs)
        ↓
Document Ingestion & Parsing
        ↓
Summarization & Insight Extraction
        ↓
RAG + Semantic Search
        ↓
Knowledge Graph (Neo4j)
        ↓
Dashboard (Search, Graphs, Reports)

## 🧩 Key Features
- AI-based research summarization
- Context-aware question answering (RAG)
- Graph-based relationship visualization
- Scalable semantic search system
- User-friendly dashboard interface

---

## 🧠 Conclusion
This project demonstrates how AI can transform research workflows by automating analysis, enabling intelligent search, and providing structured insights through knowledge graphs.